      <title>瑞银将关闭遗留房地产基金以应对写字楼市场困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/ubs-to-wind-down-legacy-real-estate-fund-on-office-market-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团将清算一只旗舰房地产基金，这是投资者从低迷的商业房地产市场撤资引发动荡的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/ubs-to-wind-down-legacy-real-estate-fund-on-office-market-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 09:28:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BayWa 在更大范围重组前获得 5.47 亿欧元救助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/baywa-stakeholders-provide-500-million-for-embattled-trader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于慕尼黑的 BayWa AG 已从其股东和贷款银行筹集了 5.47 亿欧元（6.02 亿美元）的额外流动资金，为这家资金短缺的德国大宗商品交易商提供了更多时间来组织更广泛的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/baywa-stakeholders-provide-500-million-for-embattled-trader</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 08:45:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
